      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kain Wenteris irr/ \nlihds ar wiꞥſch prett teem/ kas par Algu\nDihkus darra/ behdatees."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Wirfneeki no Zoana\nirr Gefki/ Warauis gudru Pad-\ndohma- Deweju Padohms irr\ntraks tappis. Rà warrat juhs\nno Warauis fazzihrt: Es eſmu to\nGudru Dehls/ weens Dehls to\nwezzu Kehnimu?"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kur irr nu tawee Gud-\nree? lai tee tew finnamu darra/\nfo tas KUNGS Zebnot irr no-\ndohmajs prett Egipti."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Wirfneeki no Zoana\nirr Gefki tappuschi/tee Wirfnee-\nki no Nowa irr peewilti / un\ndarra arridsan Egipti maldain/\nlihds ar to Stuhri winnas Zil-\nfchu."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr wee-\nnu pahrwehrstu Garru winno\nStarpâ islehjis/ ka tee Egipti\ndarra maldam wiſſa jawâ Dar-\nbâ/ itt ka Apdsehrits wahrtahs\njawâ Wehmekli."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tad teem Egiptereem\nne buhs nekahds Darbs / pee ka\njeb Galiwu/jeb Astu/jeb Garru/\njeb Zelinu warretu pasiht."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tai Deena tee Egipteri\nbuhs ka Seewas/ un behdatees\nun bailofees / preekſch Kustina-\nschanas tahs Rohkas ta KUN-\nGA Zebnot/ fo wiꞥſch prett teem\nkusinahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Semme Juha\nbuhs teem Egiptereem par Is-\ntrubzinaschann/ kas winnas pee-\nninehs/ tas bailofees preekſch to"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai Deenâ runnahs pe\nzi Vilſfahti Egiptes Semmê K\nnâana Wallodn / un Swehre\ntam KUNGAM Zebnot/ wee\ntaps nosaufka Ireres."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai Deenâ buhs ta\nKUNGAM weens Altaris\ngiptes Widdû/ un weena usze\nSihme pee winnas Rohbeschah\npreekſch to KUNGU."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas buhs par Sih\nun par Leezibu tam KUNGa\nEgiptes-Semmê. Jo tee breh\nus to KUNGU to Apbehdiu\ntaju deht/ un wiꞥſch fuhti\nteem weenu Pestitaju un M\nsteri/ kas tohs atpestibs."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS ta\nteem Egiptereem pasihstams/\ntee Egipteri atsihs tai Deenâ\nKUNGii/ un kalpohs winna\nar Uppuxeem un Ehdamo-Upp\nreem/ nn fohlhs tam KUNG\nSohlifchann."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fitti\ntohs Egipterus/ un dseedina\ntohs/ un tee atgreesifees pee\nKUNGA/ un wiꞥſch liſſees\nteem aisluhgtees/ un dseedina\nwinnas."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai Deenâ buhs wee\nstraigahts Zeffch no Egiptes\nAffiriju/ ka tee Affireeri Egipt\nSemmê/ un tee Egipteri Af\nra Semmê nahks/ un tee Eg\nteri lihds ar teim Affireereem\npohs (tam KUNGAM.)"
    }
  ],
